        <h1>Travel to California</h1>
        <h2><span class='x'>Pack your bags, we're going to California! :D<br>
        </span></h2>
<span class="intro">
        <p>You may be wondering, <em>why</em> should <em>I</em> go to California?<br>
What's wrong with my <strong>perfectly</strong> good home?<br>
<br>
Before I continue, let me get this straight: I'm not saying there's anything wrong with your home (unless you're living in a dump because you want to; in that case I have no idea what to say). In fact, I'm sure your house is really nice.<br>
But what's wrong with visiting new places?<br>
<br>
Here's why <strong><em>I </em></strong> believe you should go:<br>

